# Data Visualization and Storytelling

## Objective
Create meaningful visualizations and derive business insights using Tableau.

## Dataset
Superstore Sales Dataset

## Visualizations Created
1. Sales by Category
2. Profit by Category
3. Monthly Sales Trend
4. Regional Sales Analysis
5. Top 10 Customers
6. Profit by Sub-Category

## Key Insights
- Technology has the highest sales.
- West region generates maximum revenue.
- Sales peak during year-end months.
- Top customers contribute significantly to revenue.
- Some sub-categories generate losses.

## Tool Used
Tableau Public

## Outcome
Created an interactive dashboard demonstrating business insights through effective visual storytelling.